title: Edmonton Oilers ' revenue 2005 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Revenue in million U.S. dollars, containing a total of 14 data points.
In general Revenue in million U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2012/13 and 2013/14.
The highest Revenue in million U.S. dollars, of value 154.0 was reached at Year 2018/19
The lowest Revenue in million U.S. dollars, of value 71.0 was reported at Year 2006/07
